Additions (2003-0087) and (2003-0097) (2800 items, 4.4 lin. ft.; dated 1920s-2003
                  and n.d.) consists largely of manuscripts and typescripts of Bingham's poetry,
                  prose, and plays ([1970s]-2003). Also includes personal diaries, 1992-2003;
                  photographs of Bingham and her friends/family; clippings of articles and reviews;
                  an appraisal report of Wolf Pen Mill Farm (property that contains Sallie's artist
                  retreat); and a small amount of printed material and correspondence.
